            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Thanks for the tip with `reg_recording()`. I considered that solution but thought that it would make sense to solve it without relying on statusbar customization.\r\n\r\nTo be honest i can't follow your proposal entirely, so sorry if the following is redundant.\r\n\r\nPersonally i think it would be nice if the cmdline pops up for things like the recording indicator. I had another confusing situation when using `qa` to show the ascii code and it wasn't shown. Maybe i missed something in the other discussions, but i'm not sure how to work around situations like these without handling all the edge cases in my config.",
